description: American Picture House Corporation provides one-stop solutions for independent content creators in the United States. It engages in developing, packaging, financing, and producing films or shows. It is also involved in acquisition, sales/marketing, distribution, output deals, and print and advertising. The company was formerly known as Life Design Station International, Inc. and changed its name to American Picture House Corporation in April 2020. American Picture House Corporation is based in New York, New York.
